sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Sidecar as llm-d-routing-sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Allowlist as AllowlistValidator<br/>(SSRF Protection)
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller Pod<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXLv2 Protocol)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port: <prefiller:port><br/>Body: {messages, model, ...}

    alt SSRF Protection Enabled
        Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller target host
        Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Allowed / HTTP 403 Denied
    end

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(forwarded request)<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Response with kv_transfer_params<br/>{remote_block_ids, remote_engine_id,<br/>remote_host, remote_port, ...}

    Note over Sidecar: Extract kv_transfer_params<br/>from prefiller response

    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Body: original request +<br/>kv_transfer_params injected<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Inference Result<br/>(streaming or complete)
    Sidecar-->>Client: Chat Completion Response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Passthrough (No x-prefiller-host-port Header)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port header)
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward unmodified request<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Inference Result
    Sidecar-->>Client: Chat Completion Response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 3: SSRF Allowlist Updates (Background)

    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Sidecar->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Sidecar: InferencePool events<br/>(spec.selector changes)
    Sidecar->>K8sAPI: Watch Pods matching<br/>InferencePool selectors
    K8sAPI-->>Sidecar: Pod events<br/>(IPs, hostnames)
    Note over Sidecar: Update internal allowlist<br/>(30s resync period)
